                <p class="content-lg font-weight-light">
                    Jeff Green has been at the forefront of bringing people together from all areas of society for over 30 years, and as a Former MP Candidate, takes great pride in his highly influential personal network. Currently, he is writing "Making the cake bigger" a book providing Business Leaders the tools to improve social mobility impact and achieving revenue growth through diversity.
                </p>
                <p class="content-lg font-weight-light">
                    Today, he is an angel investor focussing on investing in female Entrepreneurs which directly links to his leadership initiative - BalancedBoards.net. Here, his team recruits leaders from all backgrounds into Non Executive and Director positions in both listed and unlisted companies, focusing on gender, ethnicity and faith diversity.
                </p>
                <p class="content-lg font-weight-light">
                    Jeff mentors tomorrow's leaders with his work with HRH Prince of Wales's charity the Mosaic Network as an Awards Judge Chair and has been nominated for a Diversity Lifetime Achievement Award. He is a Member of The Chartered Institute of Securities & Investment.
                </p>
                <p class="content-lg font-weight-light">
                    Jeffrey Green is a General Partner at Markhor Capital and cares deeply about gender diversity.
                </p>
